SINGER: ♪ All night,
give me mad love ♪

41:11.599 --> 41:14.123
♪ All night,
give me mad love ♪

41:14.167 --> 41:16.648
♪ Yeah, don't let me down,
do-do-down ♪

41:16.691 --> 41:18.954
♪ All night,
give me mad love ♪

41:18.998 --> 41:21.348
♪ All night,
give me mad love ♪

41:21.391 --> 41:23.568
♪ All night,
give me mad love ♪

41:23.611 --> 41:25.483
♪ Yeah, don't let me down,
do-do-down ♪

41:29.574 --> 41:30.879
LEON: Julia.

41:36.232 --> 41:37.451
Orange soda.

41:37.495 --> 41:41.455
It used to make everything
feel better.

41:41.499 --> 41:42.891
When I was 11.

41:45.459 --> 41:47.156
Worth a shot.

41:50.551 --> 41:53.946
I-I had no idea
things would take such a turn.

41:53.989 --> 41:57.210
I mean, it's amazing how cruel
people can be on the Internet.

41:57.253 --> 41:59.517
And you know, I never thought

41:59.560 --> 42:02.258
that you would have to pay
such a public price.

42:04.347 --> 42:07.176
And I'm s...

42:09.439 --> 42:11.267
Here?

42:11.311 --> 42:12.921
Well,
I guess that's as close

42:12.965 --> 42:14.488
to an apology as I'm gonna get.

42:14.532 --> 42:17.578
Julia, can I--can I come--

42:19.624 --> 42:21.539
I don't think we're there yet.

42:23.236 --> 42:26.108
Sorry.
Good night, Dad.

42:30.199 --> 42:33.507
SINGER: ♪ I never go back,
no, no, no ♪

42:33.551 --> 42:36.336
♪ I never go,
I never go back ♪

42:36.379 --> 42:39.469
♪ I never go back,
no, no, no ♪

42:39.513 --> 42:42.472
♪ I never go,
I never go back ♪

42:45.127 --> 42:47.434
I think we found
your new key witness--

42:47.477 --> 42:49.262
waiting in your office.

42:49.305 --> 42:50.655
Really?

42:50.698 --> 42:52.700
Maybe we won't need
that continuance after all.

42:59.402 --> 43:00.665
Mr. and Mrs. Doyle.

43:00.708 --> 43:03.058
Nice to meet you.

43:03.102 --> 43:05.321
We're here to help.

43:05.365 --> 43:08.586
I'd like to testify
against Leon Bechley.

